{"tid":1595453,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[MMORPG] 科隆 Corum Online 私服 - Kaien's Revenge Server","createTime":"2019-09-26T05:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T16:49:40.000Z","uid":69212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b41c878e51174d8797ab4a935578b9a8f7d1614","tid":1595453,"uid":69212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBo5ozX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBo5ozX.png&h=a0da72f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n            Corum Online是一款新型態線上遊戲，本作除了在2003年於日、韓上市時引起矚目之外，也被評為2003年最有內容的重點遊戲。<br />\n            本作故事背景圍繞在AFONONTRIA大陸的第三世紀，達斯泰德意圖侵占水晶封印的魔力，使得大陸瀕臨崩解。在聖騎士隊的號召下，英雄們深入蠻荒地下城，搜尋水晶、奪取要地以正面迎抗達斯泰德。<br />\n            在「Corum」中，有多達3000個地下城可供玩家探險，皆為經濟和軍事的重要領地，並可以佔領經營。同盟或領地的擴大會影響到領土主的整體實力。玩家在本作中是扮演領土主或遊俠，在深入各式各樣的地下城冒險旅途。<br />\n<br />\n正服官網： <a href=\"http://corum.saga-city.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorum.saga-city.com&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=e4f3b1c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://corum.saga-city.com</a> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">私服名稱：Kaien's Revenge</span></span><br />\n語言：英文<br />\n網站：<a href=\"https://www.kaiensrevenge.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kaiensrevenge.com&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=5de07cbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kaiensrevenge.com</a><br />\n臉書社團：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/kaiensrevenge/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fkaiensrevenge%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=0df9f60a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/kaiensrevenge/?ref=share</a><br />\n下載網址：<a href=\"https://www.kaiensrevenge.com/getting-started/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kaiensrevenge.com%2Fgetting-started%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=6c390b2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kaiensrevenge.com/getting-started/</a><br />\n註冊方式：直接在帳號及密碼的欄位輸入相關資訊即可<br />\n更新資訊：GM正在開發新裝備，新box，新守護，新地圖及修正一些錯誤，預計近期會套用，敬請期待！<br />\n遊戲影片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=kaien+revenge\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fresults%3Fsearch_query%3Dkaien%2Brevenge&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=bf1c3c88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=kaien+revenge</a><br />\n<br />\n福利：EXP, 裝備掉落, 衝裝機率大幅提高, 物價低, 假日EXP Double<br />\nTg：fkthepopox2<br />\n有問題可以係到留言/ TG我"},{"pid":"2ec35a17b6d183da948386d0e30f330c53e84dce","tid":1595453,"uid":69212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"隻Game都好舊, 10幾年前<br />\n希望搵得返以前台服D老手"},{"pid":"8189cab9d0bf9a6ebce4fc03ddf732b517b276ac","tid":1595453,"uid":69212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"新手都非常歡迎<br />\n不過要D時間上手"},{"pid":"dea7cf4553097f9dcff3fd125948ffa3960d5c9c","tid":1595453,"uid":69212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人會玩online game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ac64cff9d1c5ba3b85e12913138ce1a855f916","tid":1595453,"uid":69212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"有冇老手相認"},{"pid":"7e31b2bac8cc7c9816e666926fa11d055b770d74","tid":1595453,"uid":69212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"輕鬆單機冇難度<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"2def2e9d3157c018eb1708d223d321cae38a2cdd","tid":1595453,"uid":69212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:07:59.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"17040a8575bdfdf9623d3a4ee7df917c429571fb","tid":1595453,"uid":69212,"like":0,